## ğŸ—ï¸ **System Architecture**


```mermaid
graph TB
    A[React Frontend] --> B[API Gateway]
    B --> C[HealthSync AI]
    B --> D[ProfessionSync AI]
    B --> E[KnowledgeSync AI]
    B --> F[FinanceSync AI]
    B --> G[SocialSync AI]
    
    H[Redis Message Bus] --> C
    H --> D
    H --> E
    H --> F
    H --> G
    
    I[MongoDB] --> B
    J[Unified Calendar] --> A
```


### ğŸª **The Five AI Agents**

| AI Agent | Domain | Key Features | Inter-AI Examples |
|----------|--------|--------------|-------------------|
| ğŸ¥ **HealthSync** | Health & Wellness | Symptom tracking, medication reminders, fitness planning | Tells ProfessionSync about sick days |
| ğŸ’¼ **ProfessionSync** | Career & Work | Project management, skill development, meeting coordination | Gets health data for workload adjustment |
| ğŸ§  **KnowledgeSync** | Learning & Growth | Course tracking, research assistance, skill progression | Aligns learning with career goals |
| ğŸ’° **FinanceSync** | Money & Budget | Expense tracking, investment monitoring, financial planning | Shares budget constraints with all AIs |
| ğŸ‘¥ **SocialSync** | Relationships & Events | Social calendar, networking, event planning | Coordinates social time with work schedule |



## ğŸ’» **Tech Stack**

### **Frontend**
```typescript
React 18           // Modern component architecture
Redux Toolkit      // Centralized state management
Material-UI        // Consistent design system
Socket.io Client   // Real-time AI communication
TypeScript         // Type-safe development
```

### **Backend Microservices**
```javascript
Node.js + Express  // 5 independent microservices
API Gateway        // Central routing & authentication
Socket.io          // Real-time inter-AI messaging
Redis              // Message bus & caching
MongoDB            // Document storage
JWT Auth           // Secure authentication
```

### **AI & Integration**
```python
OpenAI GPT-4       // Natural language processing
Custom Prompts     // Specialized AI personalities
External APIs      // Health, Finance, Calendar
Event-Driven       // Reactive AI communication
```

### **DevOps & Infrastructure**
```yaml
Docker             # Containerized deployment
GitHub Actions     # CI/CD pipeline
Jest + Supertest   # Comprehensive testing
ESLint + Prettier  # Code quality
Vercel/AWS         # Cloud deployment
```

