## ğŸ”’ **Security & Privacy**

### **Data Protection**
- ğŸ” **Domain Isolation**: Each AI only accesses relevant data
- ğŸ”’ **Encrypted Communication**: Secure messaging between services
- ğŸ‘¤ **User Control**: Granular permissions for AI data sharing
- ğŸŒ **GDPR Compliant**: Right to deletion and data portability

### **Security Architecture**
- ğŸ›¡ï¸ **JWT Authentication**: Secure access across microservices
- âš¡ **Rate Limiting**: API protection and abuse prevention
- ğŸ§¹ **Input Sanitization**: Safe data handling across all AIs
- ğŸ“‹ **Audit Logging**: Complete tracking of inter-AI decisions

